title: Hamilton Beach  6 speed hand mixer with quick burst 62647
description: Hamilton Beach  6 speed hand mixer with quick burst 62647
transcripts:
The Hamilton Beach hand mixer with the quick burst button provides extra power at any speed. With 300 watts of peak power and six speeds, you'll mix creams to batters with ease. There is a rubber grip handle and a bowl rest feature to make mixing more comfortable. 

You'll get two beaters, a whisk, and two dough hooks with the mixer. And the attachments and mixer all pack away nicely in their own storage case. For all your mixing needs, the Hamilton Beach hand mixer is a must have in the kitchen. Now that's good thinking.
